<li id="cite_note-Reborn-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Reborn_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Reborn_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Reborn_4-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFMorrison2010" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Grant_Morrison" title="Grant Morrison">Morrison, Grant</a> (April 7, 2010). <i><a href="/wiki/Batman_and_Robin_(comic_book)#Collected_editions" title="Batman and Robin (comic book)">Batman and Robin: Batman Reborn&#8211;Deluxe Edition</a>&#8211;"Batman Redrawn"</i>. <a href="/wiki/DC_Comics" title="DC Comics">DC Comics</a>. p.&#160;164. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-4012-2566-7" title="Special:BookSources/1-4012-2566-7"><bdi>1-4012-2566-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Batman+and+Robin%3A+Batman+Reborn%26ndash%3BDeluxe+Edition%26ndash%3B%22Batman+Redrawn%22&amp;rft.pages=164&amp;rft.pub=DC+Comics&amp;rft.date=2010-04-07&amp;rft.isbn=1-4012-2566-7&amp;rft.aulast=Morrison&amp;rft.aufirst=Grant&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AProfessor+Pyg" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
</li>
